# COMPONENT

## NamedViewSample

### PACKAGE

org.sample.viewdefinition

### DESCRIPTION

Named view definition sample component.

### SPECIFICATION

This component demonstrates explicit named view aliases on top of the generated `ENTITY > VIEW` read surface.
The first line is runtime-light: named views reuse the generated projection and select it through the CNCF view DSL.

# ENTITY

## Person

### DESCRIPTION

Person record used as the source entity for named view selection.

### ATTRIBUTE

| name  | type     | multiplicity |
|-------+----------+--------------|
| id    | entityid | 1            |
| name  | name     | 1            |
| city  | string   | 1            |
| title | string   | 1            |

### VIEW

- VIEWS :: summary, detail
- EVENTS :: person.created, person.updated
- REBUILDABLE :: true

#### DESCRIPTION

The explicit view definition registers named aliases and custom query metadata while keeping the first-line projection shape identical to the default view.

#### ATTRIBUTE

| name  | type     | multiplicity |
|-------+----------+--------------|
| id    | entityid | 1            |
| name  | name     | 1            |
| city  | string   | 1            |
| title | string   | 1            |

#### QUERY

##### searchByCity

- EXPRESSION :: person.city == query.city
